Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:45.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Collins, you musn't dash out like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Heroman! Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was for the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:26.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it now that she's seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:30.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It seems like she \Nwas a big Heroman fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:32.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:37.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I bet she'd be more useful than \Nthe Professor when the chips are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Joey, Psy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for a swim together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we still have Will to deal with. \NCan't blame you for being concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is that, and this is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach, swimsuits, Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What else do you need, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have fun when \Nit's time to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body ain't gonna hold \Nup otherwise, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:35.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You have permission to have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've all come to a southern island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:07.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes arranged for us all to go to \Nthis government owned, uninhabited island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, with no other people\Non the island to worry about,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we're having a lot of fun here with Heroman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:39.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... I'm really enjoying myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This stuff's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:54.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:24.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, I'm surprised the \Ngovernment has an island like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:28.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. They say the \Nworld's in a recession,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess that only \Napplies to certain places.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If those funds could have been\Nused for my research instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to this, we're\Nfinally able to have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,without worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're satisfied already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...has only begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:01.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning on doing, Psy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not some freaky ceremony or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the beach, swimsuits, and a \Nbarbecue, this comes next, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to clarify... What \Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost stories, man! Ghost stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:27.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a story I heard from one of the \NNIA staff on the charter plane here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:32.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the government bought this \Nisland, it wasn't uninhabited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There were definitely people living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason that those people \Nvanished from this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is because of a legend long told here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The curse of the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that anyone who \Nsets eyes on the demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:58.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,will meet with death soon \Nafterwards, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what began happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the growing number of victims,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:09.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the inhabitants of the island \Nwere faced with two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get cursed and throw away their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,or abandon the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why this island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Everyone's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:24.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for the demon, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on Professor. \NThe story's just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a self-styled child of science!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not about me, and continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, behind you! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon always appears on \Nhot, humid nights like tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the right humidity, but \Nit only shows up on windy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Psy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say windy... You \Nmean windy like it is, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:37.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... About like this, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:46.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, Mr. Denton. This story \Nis a work of fiction, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:50.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-R-R-R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And it's not like the lights \Nare turning on and off for no reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:58.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,or we're hearing rumbling sounds \Nfrom far away... So, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lights are turning on and off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a rumbling sound from far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-W-W-W-What's this mean, Psy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:18.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard about it, is all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How does the story continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the name of the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That name of the demon is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shapeshifter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the name says, it \Ncan change its form at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it shows itself as the thing the \Npeople it curses fear the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the most fearful \Nperson in the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,from the darkness on the \Nother side of the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Mr. Denton!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:21.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be anyone on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Heroman... A-A-A...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something not right about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:45.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everyone's scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean the story is too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:55.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you heard this ghost story\Nfrom a person from the NIA, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What must be it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-So-So-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:07.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being set up by \Nthat person from the NIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Candid camera, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Candid camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise this story \Nmatches up way too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:18.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going exactly as Psy's story said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:22.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet when we open this door, \Nthey'll be all like "surprise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Joey's friends will come rushing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:27.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:31.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-Y-Y-You're going to open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:35.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Run for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Run for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful when you move him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Denton, get the first-aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:00.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. This is the \Nlodge. There's no danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It'll be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:05.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:08.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The others must have already evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:12.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only ones left on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Push myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get out of \Nhere. Everyone, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We had... an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:38.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, right now we...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:43.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. If you are also a scientist, \Nyou should explain the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll do it on the \Nway. Hurry and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:14.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Up we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:25.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is really strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:34.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That better be true, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away from the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:24.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina... Lina. Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:34.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:42.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's all right now, Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina... Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:56.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I got saved by you again, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Joey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:47.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where everyone went?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:56.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing. I'll go look for them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here, Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:08.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you, Joey. So... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:13.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:54.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:58.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know. We were \Nsuddenly attacked, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...everyone got split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think everyone should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:08.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That scientist told us \Nto head to the airfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:10.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I bet that's what they're all doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:14.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is somebody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:31.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you... You were safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:34.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one you saved earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Lavi, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Joseph Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:52.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:57.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's too early to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:05.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:08.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're through!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:52.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.48,0:23:57.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman, I'll save you! Count on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:24:01.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a biohazard where plants have been \Ntransformed into living, willful weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The party has been split \Nup thanks to its attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to set things in order,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey and Heroman head toward \Nthe center of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:15.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #19: Survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
